devOps/agile practices for software development

CI/CD pipeline:
-----------------------
Automated pipeline which provides quick feedback (in the form of notification) (twice a day). Manual way is less productive.
a runnable specification of the steps 

Continuous Integration: Build, Run the test
Continuous Deployment/Delivery: Deploys a new version of the application (CD) to an Env/Infrastructure.

central repository - Code changes are merged multiple times a day.

Trigger: new code merge / auto-schedule / manual initiation / result of other pipeline

Build Stage -> Test Stage ->

Build Stage: compile -> build docker image -> 

Test Stage: Run Automated Tests / Junits / Integration 









